data.output: I went to buy a new car. When I reached there I forgot whether I should buy the car with petrol or diesel. I figured it out after asking my friend on phone. He also mentioned about the differnent pump types in different cars.
I asked my friend about sending the letter as I was new in the country. He told me how to stamp the letter and and how can I send it by the post. I finally had a good understanding about it.

I told my friend that I was working with different survey platforms. I told her about what should I do to a survey asking about to write a story  containing three words: organ, empire and comply. I literally had no idea, what to write about but I figured out a nice idea that I used to do it.

My friend said three words when we were playing chinese whisper. I had no idea what did she say but I herd some of it. On my turn I said the words bloom, cavemen, exist. Finally I came to know that the words were gloom, payment and exist.
